a=10
b=20
'''c=a-b if a>b else c=b-a
print(c)'''
#In this short hand if-else syntax, "we can't assign the variables with values", if we try to assign based on condition, it will raise an "error"
'''instead we can use the following short hand if else syntax...'''
if a>b:c=a-b
else:c=b-a
print(c)
'''_____________OUTPUT_____________
10

[Program finished]'''
